• Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - Transport Minister Fikile Mbalula is meeting with traffic officials following this weekend's horrific accidents in Limpopo. On Sunday, 24 people died following a crash between a bus and a taxi on the R81 in Maphalle. READ: 24 killed in crash outside Tzaneen A number of people were also injured and taken to hospital.